ry mountain."},{"version":"x","text":"It rescues people stranded by blizzards in the mountains. Its shaggy fur shields it from the cold."},{"version":"y","text":"Being wrapped in its long fur is so comfortable that a person would be fine even overnight on a wintry mountain."},{"version":"omega-ruby","text":"It rescues people stranded by blizzards in the mountains. Its shaggy fur shields it from the cold."},{"version":"alpha-sapphire","text":"Being wrapped in its long fur is so comfortable that a person would be fine even overnight on a wintry mountain."},{"version":"sun","text":"Intelligent, good-natured, and valiant, it\u2019s a trustworthy partner on rescue teams."},{"version":"moon","text":"With this wise Pok\u00e9mon, there could be no concern that it would ever attack people. Some parents even trust it to babysit."},{"version":"ultra-sun","text":"It pays no mind to the cold, thanks to its long warm coat. Stoutland in Alola look a little uncomfortable."},{"version":"ultra-moon","text":"Its fur is long and thick. A long time ago in cold regions, every household kept a Stoutland."},{"version":"sword","text":"These Pok\u00e9mon seem to enjoy living with humans. Even a Stoutland caught in the wild will warm up to people in about three days."},{"version":"shield","text":"Stoutland is immensely proud of its impressive moustache. It\u2019s said that moustache length is what determines social standing among this species."}],"evo":{"name":"lillipup","level":0,"min_level":null,"trigger":null,"item":null,"held_item":null,"known_move":null,"known_move_type":null,"location":null,"min_affection":null,"min_beauty":null,"min_happiness":null,"needs_overworld_rain":false,"time_of_day":null,"turn_upside_down":false,"evolves_to":[{"name":"herdier","level":1,"min_level":16,"trigger":"level-up","item":null,"held_item":null,"known_move":null,"known_move_type":null,"location":null,"min_affection":null,"min_beauty":null,"min_happiness":null,"needs_overworld_rain":false,"time_of_day":"",